1.5.0
- Fix details date missing (not being parsed correctly it seems)
- Add new style app icon.
- Fix download progress not displaying in notification bar while downloading.
- Upon start, check if a valid download mirror is set, otherwise use first from list.
- Move all inner ResponseTask classes into their own classes.
- Maybe format some file details content better, like some credits that seem to lack newlines.

1.6.0
- Tabs to bottom navigation, use side menu to store settings and about. Use new style of navigation.
- Support dark theme (theme from Theme.MaterialComponents.DayNight.DarkActionBar and fix issues)
